{"title":"博客配置修改","date":"2020-08-19T04:16:53.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Aug 19, 2020","L":"08/19/2020","MM-DD":"08-19"},"link":"qtd9qr","comments":true,"tags":["daily"],"categories":["daily"],"updated":"2021-02-03T04:21:00.601Z","content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.yzh.im/about/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">https://www.yzh.im/about/</a></p>\n<a id=\"more\"></a>\n<h1 id=\"语雀防盗链和行内公式\">语雀防盗链和行内公式<a title=\"#语雀防盗链和行内公式\" href=\"#语雀防盗链和行内公式\"></a></h1>\n<p>问题 语雀同步之后 latex 公式以图片的形式嵌入在了 md 文档中</p>\n<ol>\n<li>语雀的图片做了防盗链处理, 无法访问, 导致公式无法显示</li>\n<li>该主题的图片不能在行内显示, 也就是说尺寸比较小的图片都只能独行显示.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>解决方法</p>\n<ol>\n<li>防盗链问题: <a href=\"https://github.com/x-cold/yuque-hexo/issues/41\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\">https://github.com/x-cold/yuque-hexo/issues/41</a> 看不懂</li>\n<li>图片行内显示问题: css+html, 我在 css 文件中写了</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight css\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"selector-tag\">img</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">  <span class=\"attribute\">display</span>: inline-block;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>虽然是看起来是这么写,但是没什么卵用, 不知道怎么解决</p>\n<h1 id=\"修改\">修改<a title=\"#修改\" href=\"#修改\"></a></h1>\n<p>问题一解决了, 可算让我找到了插入的地方<br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/1552854/1597810652853-b6649db9-3646-4205-9ef4-809236f1795b.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1080&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;originHeight=1080&amp;originWidth=1920&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=1920\" alt=\"\"><br>\n问题二也解决了<br>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2020/png/1552854/1597810652788-d4c1c107-cd85-4305-aab5-c94d5e53292c.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=1080&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;originHeight=1080&amp;originWidth=1920&amp;size=0&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=1920\" alt=\"\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">路径themes\\yun\\layout\\_partial\\layout.pug</span><br><span class=\"line\">meta(name&#x3D;&quot;referrer&quot; content&#x3D;&quot;no-referrer&quot;)</span><br><span class=\"line\">路径: themes\\yun\\scripts\\filters\\index.js</span><br><span class=\"line\">style&#x3D;&quot;display: inline-block; vertical-align:middle&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"实现主题标题跳转到语雀\">实现主题标题跳转到语雀<a title=\"#实现主题标题跳转到语雀\" href=\"#实现主题标题跳转到语雀\"></a></h1>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/1552854/1609779477950-72aa2912-9161-4246-918a-903583890127.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=143&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=286&amp;originWidth=997&amp;size=20323&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=498.5\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>\n路径: <code>themes\\yun\\layout\\_partial\\post\\post-edit.pug</code></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">a.post -</span><br><span class=\"line\">  edit -</span><br><span class=\"line\">  link(</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (href = theme.post_edit.url + <span class=\"string\">&quot;/&quot;</span> + page.urlname),</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (target = <span class=\"string\">&quot;_blank&quot;</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (title = __(<span class=\"string\">&quot;post.edit&quot;</span>)),</span><br><span class=\"line\">    (rel = <span class=\"string\">&quot;noopener&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">  ) +</span><br><span class=\"line\">  icon(<span class=\"string\">&quot;icon-edit-line&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//- a.post-edit-link(href=theme.post_edit.url + page.source, target=&#x27;_blank&#x27;, title=__(&#x27;post.edit&#x27;), rel=&#x27;noopener&#x27;)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//-   +icon(&#x27;icon-edit-line&#x27;)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h1 id=\"解决-localsearch-的相对地址问题\">解决 localsearch 的相对地址问题<a title=\"#解决-localsearch-的相对地址问题\" href=\"#解决-localsearch-的相对地址问题\"></a></h1>\n<p>地址 <code>themes\\yun\\source\\js\\search\\local-search.js</code></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2021/png/1552854/1609918486775-8780333b-50f7-4e34-a7bb-ef71fb27d104.png#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=77&amp;margin=%5Bobject%20Object%5D&amp;name=image.png&amp;originHeight=153&amp;originWidth=1278&amp;size=24302&amp;status=done&amp;style=none&amp;width=639\" alt=\"image.png\" class=\"φcx\"></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight javascript\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">//str += `&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;$&#123;data_url&#125;&quot; class=&quot;search-result-title&quot;&gt;$&#123;data_title&#125;&lt;/a&gt;`;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">str += <span class=\"string\">`&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;<span class=\"subst\">$&#123;data_url.substring(</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"><span class=\"subst\">  <span class=\"number\">1</span>,</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"><span class=\"subst\">  data_url.length</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\"><span class=\"subst\">)&#125;</span>&quot; class=&quot;search-result-title&quot;&gt;<span class=\"subst\">$&#123;data_title&#125;</span>&lt;/a&gt;`</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div><h1 id=\"推荐文章\">推荐文章<a title=\"#推荐文章\" href=\"%e6%8e%a8%e8%8d%90%e6%96%87%e7%ab%a0\"></a></h1><ul><li><a href=\"https://mvbbb.github.io/my2020/\">Bye! My 2020</a></li><li><a href=\"https://mvbbb.github.io/gmx84f/\">近期规划-碎碎念</a></li><li><a href=\"https://mvbbb.github.io/taxvu3/\">刷题!刷题!</a></li><li><a href=\"https://mvbbb.github.io/mce5h4/\">想学算法</a></li></ul></div>","prev":{"title":"Java 细节","link":"nwg3e5"},"next":{"title":"自顶向下与自底向上","link":"aa32vk"},"plink":"https://mvbbb.github.io/qtd9qr/","toc":[{"id":"语雀防盗链和行内公式","title":"语雀防盗链和行内公式","index":"1"},{"id":"修改","title":"修改","index":"2"},{"id":"实现主题标题跳转到语雀","title":"实现主题标题跳转到语雀","index":"3"},{"id":"解决-localsearch-的相对地址问题","title":"解决 localsearch 的相对地址问题","index":"4"},{"id":"推荐文章","title":"推荐文章","index":"5"}],"copyright":{"author":"Mvbbb","link":"<a href=\"https://mvbbb.github.io/qtd9qr/\" title=\"博客配置修改\">https://mvbbb.github.io/qtd9qr/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"}}